name: FOUND! (Genesis Piece)
description: Re-minting of my first ever NFT, dropped on Hic et Nunc in 30 March 2021 and burned unsold. This edition is a new development processed from the original raw file with upsampling, noise cancellation and color enhancement. Shot 1st February 2011 in the Lapa commercial district of São Paulo in front of a clothing store just before opening. Location: -23.519483, -46.702671.
